            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils d'Apoll<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de Theud<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils d'
            Hagèsistratos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils d'Eirènaios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils d'Aristoboulos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de Sôdamos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 
            fils de Peisis, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de Theudotos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de Dexilas, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Apoll<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Theud<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of
            Hagesistratos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Eirenaios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Aristoboulos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Sodamos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 
            son of Peisis, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Theudotos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Dexilas, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Apoll<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Theud<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di
            Hagesistratos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Eirenaios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Aristoboulos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Sodamos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 
            figlio di Peisis, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Theudotos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Dexilas, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ios, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>This might belong to a list of ephebes dedicating to Hermes and Heracles the names of their officers. But there are also other possibilities.</p>
	   <p>All names are already attested at Cyrene, but for <foreign xml:lang="grc">Δεξίλας</foreign>, a semantic variant of the already attested 
	       <foreign xml:lang="grc">Δεξίδαμος</foreign>.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
